      "text": "血管扩张症等）。",
      "is_heading": false
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        62.784000396728516,
        287.0189208984375,
        294.9100036621094,
        297.57891845703125
      ],
      "max_font_size": 10.5600004196167,
      "text": "（十）严重慢性肝衰竭",
